[LONG DESC]
<h2>Description</h2>
<p>Teaches <a href="/dp/moves/facade">Facade</a> to a Pokemon when used. One-time use.</p>

<p>An attack move that doubles its power if the user is poisoned, paralyzed, or has a burn.</p>